          "scid": "sn56.76:1.1",
          "pli": "… “Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appakā te sattā ye pharusāya vācāya paṭiviratā; atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye pharusāya vācāya appaṭiviratā … pe …. ",
